id":230392,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發雞盲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最多值一毫，點睇都無2蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一毫子都大過佢果粒野"},{"pid":"057bbae4cc9ce1851bce86863234cf8e0e8f3271","tid":230392,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拮爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會失血過多致死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bf01470484e602c3b925661f9dbd51cb0c7486","tid":230392,"uid":87395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"好想幫你擠爆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63950503fa97c49c6b94396229f8b9ce1a99e8d8","tid":230392,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"果個位似係 「過濾性病毒疣」<br />\n雞眼同疣似樣<br />\n雞眼只係皮膚經常磨擦受壓，皮膚組織增生變硬，用刀（𠝹表皮）或者用手me走就會好返<br />\n相反，過濾性病毒疣係因為身體抵抗力變差而產生，要用冷凍療法or電療or強力果酸去清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者用刀連肉𠝹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但痛到仆街同流勁多血，但小心病毒疣條根生到好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成棵樹根咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且有傳染性，隻手hi到都會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你似係周圍摸摸到（抵抗力差果時）<br />\n<br />\n利伸：中過疣，成隻腳板都係，用果酸溶成個月腳板，痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b444e05f255019b193ef340ec673c4b22b2294","tid":230392,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"我係泳池赤腳沖涼出事"},{"pid":"356ae2a3db8c381475dba0a5ecef5632d5fd4278","tid":230392,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"一係就雞眼<br />\n一係就毛囊炎<br />\n去睇下醫生食消炎藥<br />\n如果係雞眼去藥房買雞眼藥水<br />\n拿到仆街但好快好"}]}